             was indicted, for <rs id="t17880227-15-off76" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17880227-15-off76" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17880227-15-off76" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling house of 
                     
