                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880227-15-victim208 t17880227-15-viclabel77"></join>, on the <rs id="t17880227-15-cd78" type="crimeDate">24th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880227-15-off76 t17880227-15-cd78"></join>, about the hour of seven in the night, and stealing ten yards of printed calico, value 20 s. the property of the said Mary
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17880227-15-person209">
                  DANIEL
                   TURNER
               <interp inst="t17880227-15-person209" type="surname" value="TURNER"></interp>
